10
00:01:05,910 --> 00:01:08,940
Why are you so surprised? It's making me feel bad.

11
00:01:14,260 --> 00:01:16,330
I didn't know that I would see you here.

12
00:01:18,550 --> 00:01:22,940
What can I do when the mountain (Da Hyeon) is not moving? So I had to come.

13
00:01:27,240 --> 00:01:32,580
Let's just go, shall we? I don't have the luxury to accommodate your situation right now.

14
00:01:32,580 --> 00:01:33,960
Oh?

15
00:01:35,390 --> 00:01:37,170
Should I carry you?

16
00:01:58,630 --> 00:02:00,160
Are you dating anyone?

17
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:01,730
Nope.

18
00:02:01,730 --> 00:02:04,530
That's good. I'm not either.

19
00:02:05,450 --> 00:02:07,580
Really?

20
00:02:07,580 --> 00:02:09,260
I don't think so.

21
00:02:10,330 --> 00:02:16,600
I really don't have one. Unlike someone, I didn't ride home with anyone.

22
00:02:16,600 --> 00:02:21,080
At least I didn't shop around with someone smiling ear to ear.

23
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:25,990
What are you talking about? Who did you see me shopping—

24
00:02:25,990 --> 00:02:28,230
Oh! Really.

25
00:02:28,230 --> 00:02:29,250
Oh-oh?

26
00:02:29,250 --> 00:02:32,760
What? You didn't see us enter the hotel room together?

27
00:02:34,410 --> 00:02:35,560
Stop the car.

28
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:37,690
She's my little sister

29
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:40,250
